WEBVTT

00:00:03.100 --> 00:00:06.521
You have come here to learn something,

00:00:06.601 --> 00:00:17.554
to go deep into your experiences of the knowledge of your roots.

00:00:17.634 --> 00:00:23.187
Shri Krishna has said that this is a tree

00:00:23.267 --> 00:00:32.587
which is upside down: the roots are
upwards and the leaves are outwards.

00:00:32.667 --> 00:00:38.487
In the same way, you know that Kundalini, really,

00:00:38.567 --> 00:00:43.634
when it rises in the Sahasrara or above Sahasrara,

00:00:44.033 --> 00:00:49.267
then you start getting the feeling of Kundalini.

00:00:50.367 --> 00:00:57.087
So one has to understand that when
we are now getting subtler and subtler

00:00:57.167 --> 00:00:59.721
and trying to feel the Kundalini,

00:00:59.801 --> 00:01:05.354
we should try to get out of a materialistic attitude

00:01:05.434 --> 00:01:10.400
and materialistic viewpoint and materialistic sticking point.

00:01:12.434 --> 00:01:17.387
I met one guru before – because you know I went to all of them – and

00:01:17.467 --> 00:01:21.354
I asked one of them, I said, “Why do you take money,

00:01:21.434 --> 00:01:25.521
so much money from these people who are Western people?

00:01:25.601 --> 00:01:29.387
So much, why do you take and just they become beggars,

00:01:29.467 --> 00:01:31.454
absolutely like beggars they become,

00:01:31.534 --> 00:01:36.187
because you charge them so much and so heavily?”

00:01:36.267 --> 00:01:40.667
And he told Me that, “Unless and until you make them beggars,

00:01:41.067 --> 00:01:46.521
they will never take to God. They are too rich to be near God.”

00:01:46.601 --> 00:01:52.521
I mean, this explanation I just could not understand. It was absurd.

00:01:52.601 --> 00:01:58.120
I could not understand: How can this
explanation have any proper meaning,

00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:01.454
that you should make people beggars and then they’ll be nearer to God?

00:02:01.534 --> 00:02:08.154
I said, “In India we have many beggars; do
you think those beggars are nearer to God?”

00:02:08.234 --> 00:02:12.187
So he said, “No, otherwise, you
see, they get stuck up with their money

00:02:12.267 --> 00:02:18.133
and you must just make them absolutely
without any money – moneyless people.”

00:02:19.601 --> 00:02:27.387
So, I mean, of course to such a stupid person what can you talk, and

00:02:27.467 --> 00:02:31.554
what can you convince? I couldn’t say to him,

00:02:31.634 --> 00:02:37.354
“Then why are you taking the money, if you are?”

00:02:37.434 --> 00:02:41.554
Then he would have said, “Because I’m
detached.” You see, anything one can say like that.

00:02:41.634 --> 00:02:46.320
If it starts like that, you cannot just stop it.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:52.320
But one has to understand that materialism has gone into our roots.

00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:57.521
And if we have to clear out our roots, we must get out of materialism.

00:02:57.601 --> 00:03:02.254
That’s important, but that does not in any way
mean that you torture your body or anything.

00:03:02.334 --> 00:03:03.454
I don’t mean that.

00:03:03.534 --> 00:03:06.534
But what I’m saying, your attention.

00:05:42.367 --> 00:05:51.187
So now, when we are dealing with
our roots we have to be in the centre.

00:05:51.267 --> 00:05:53.421
In the core.

00:05:53.501 --> 00:06:00.087
In the core means we are taking in, sucking in

00:06:00.167 --> 00:06:06.320
the feeling, or you can say the feeling and
awareness put together⎯what do you say to that,

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:09.234
in English is there any word?

00:06:11.267 --> 00:06:15.154
Is there any word which makes awareness and feeling put together?

00:06:15.234 --> 00:06:25.454
Is there, Gavin? Experience, you can say.

00:06:25.534 --> 00:06:30.020
The experience into your awareness and feeling.

00:06:30.100 --> 00:06:34.521
You have to get the experience into your awareness and feeling.

00:06:34.601 --> 00:06:38.554
In Marathi it’s a very simple word: janiv,

00:06:38.634 --> 00:06:40.521
comes from the word ja.

00:06:40.601 --> 00:06:45.400
Ja comes from the word spontaneous.

00:06:46.534 --> 00:06:52.587
Also ja has two meanings: ja also means dnyana, is awareness,

00:06:52.667 --> 00:06:57.587
and also it means spontaneous. Janiv.

00:06:57.667 --> 00:07:04.053
So you start sucking that within yourself

00:07:04.133 --> 00:07:07.521
when you are not entangled into other things.

00:07:07.601 --> 00:07:11.601
If your attention is entangled outside, you cannot enjoy.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:15.667
So, to be lost into [that] which is samadhi, you see,

00:07:16.067 --> 00:07:21.501
is the one where your attention is
completely drowned into the experience.

00:07:22.100 --> 00:07:25.254
That is what we have to achieve.

00:07:25.334 --> 00:07:30.154
So it’s not only materialism; also emotionalism, all kinds of “isms”.

00:07:30.234 --> 00:07:37.521
We are attacked by all kind of “isms” since the
history of word started in this world, I think,

00:07:37.601 --> 00:07:46.087
and now the unholy thing that the “ism,”
the latest is, could be “Sahaja Yoga-ism.”

00:07:46.167 --> 00:07:52.601
Also could be the greatest one because now
there has to be an attack on Sahaja Yoga also.

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:58.087
In this one is that, as I told you

00:07:58.167 --> 00:08:02.354
⎯I didn’t explain it properly or you didn’t hear Me properly that day⎯

00:08:02.434 --> 00:08:10.320
that Sahaja Yoga does not mean lethargy or slowness, not at all,

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:20.220
but is a quick and a fast stepping in, into the dissolution.

00:08:20.300 --> 00:08:22.300
Very quick.

00:08:24.234 --> 00:08:28.187
And once you very quickly dissolve into it,

00:08:28.267 --> 00:08:35.254
the whole movement of your body is quick,
but not jerky – is smooth and quick. Rhythmic.

00:08:35.334 --> 00:08:37.601
Is musical.

00:08:40.367 --> 00:08:49.601
Neither it is awkward nor lethargic, but is musical.
It has a rhythm about it. Is very gracious.

00:08:50.334 --> 00:08:57.521
The whole movement of dissolution can happen to you very easily

00:08:57.601 --> 00:09:06.521
if you don’t allow your attention to be attacked by all these “isms.”

00:09:06.601 --> 00:09:10.120
There’s no end to it. I mean, if I have to write all of them, I think

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:15.120
we’ll have to need at least one
book to write all the “isms” of the world.

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:19.320
There’s no end to it, which we have created. All right.

00:09:19.400 --> 00:09:23.354
Then the worst of all is now, I think, Sahaja Yoga-ism

00:09:23.434 --> 00:09:30.421
in which, first of all, is the feeling of lethargy:

00:09:30.501 --> 00:09:36.020
“It will happen Sahaja. Sit down, Mother will do everything for you.”

00:09:36.100 --> 00:09:39.120
Another is Sahaja Yoga-egoism,

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:42.601
in which we have got one fellow lying there.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:47.601
In which people, Sahaja Yogis, get into tantrums,

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:51.020
try to show off that they are great Sahaja Yogis,

00:09:51.100 --> 00:09:55.634
[that] they have reached the third stage or
the seventh stage or whatever they may be.

00:09:57.300 --> 00:10:03.120
Now it’s good, this example is a very
good example I wish you had taken up.

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:11.154
But see the expression of the Indians, the enamoured expressions.

00:10:11.234 --> 00:10:15.354
You see, it’s so genuine, they can’t
control within themselves, seeing Me.

00:10:15.434 --> 00:10:20.053
Now, see, it’s like – I just don’t know,

00:10:20.133 --> 00:10:24.634
but people think it’s a package deal sort
of a thing. It’s so nonsensical, I tell you.

00:10:25.033 --> 00:10:28.320
That either they have to be taken out all their money,

00:10:28.400 --> 00:10:34.020
or if they are to be told: now, for puja.
All of them are paying twenty-one [rupees]

00:10:34.100 --> 00:10:39.220
because they have to do this, all this
extra work, so they are charging twenty-one.

00:10:39.300 --> 00:10:43.220
And if you tell them [it’s] for puja, they’ll even give fifty-one.

00:10:43.300 --> 00:10:49.367
But I’m told some of you have even
refused that. I mean it’s so shameful, I tell you.

00:10:51.567 --> 00:10:56.020
It’s absolutely shameful. Can you imagine?

00:10:56.100 --> 00:10:58.254
What is twenty-one rupees to you?

00:10:58.334 --> 00:10:59.554
To them it’s quite a lot.

00:10:59.634 --> 00:11:05.587
Because it’s some sort of a part of you,
you are giving, which is so nonsensical.

00:11:05.667 --> 00:11:12.267
Just is a feeling. Is a sign of complete negativity.

00:11:13.601 --> 00:11:18.254
Left Nabhi. It’s a problem. Materialism, it’s complete materialism.

00:11:18.334 --> 00:11:25.320
Those who have been, say, doing vegetarianism are materialists.

00:11:25.400 --> 00:11:35.454
In India, we have seen the cases like, you see,
the Jains and the Marwaris and the Gujaratis,

00:11:35.534 --> 00:11:41.387
they’re all vegetarians, supposed to be very compassionate people.

00:11:41.467 --> 00:11:46.187
They build some temples also, and
sometimes they give to poor people also

00:11:46.267 --> 00:11:50.667
and sometimes to people like
Hare-Rama-Hare-Krishna who are begging in India.

00:11:51.067 --> 00:11:55.053
They give money to them. Supposed to be very compassionate.

00:11:55.133 --> 00:12:01.567
They’re more compassionate to chickens
than to human beings. We have that kind.

00:12:02.300 --> 00:12:06.087
And the same kind I have seen in the West, also.

00:12:06.167 --> 00:12:11.434
Such materialistic people, I mean, they have no shame.

00:12:12.601 --> 00:12:19.087
So when you just turn and see that, you should abhor that. Abhor it.

00:12:19.167 --> 00:12:25.521
It’s shameful! How could you be like that even in Sahaja Yoga?

00:12:25.601 --> 00:12:31.454
So as I have told you, there’s some people who are materialistic,

00:12:31.534 --> 00:12:37.567
some people who are emotionalistic,
and some people who are egoistical.

00:12:38.167 --> 00:12:44.354
Now leave all these things on the sides, then you come in the centre.

00:12:44.434 --> 00:12:46.421
Now, you are in the centre.

00:12:46.501 --> 00:12:54.220
In the centre, people enjoy just the love
of their Mother, like Shri Ganesha does.

00:12:54.300 --> 00:12:58.467
Just think how your Mother loves you. Finished. Can you?

00:12:59.300 --> 00:13:02.320
It’s a very sweet feeling.

00:13:02.400 --> 00:13:05.421
And who is your Mother, if you really believe in Her,

00:13:05.501 --> 00:13:09.601
in Sahaja Yoga, these two things should solve the problem.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:12.087
No more thinking.

00:13:12.167 --> 00:13:14.454
Just think how much your Mother loves.

00:13:14.534 --> 00:13:18.053
That means you are jumping onto My Kundalini,

00:13:18.133 --> 00:13:24.601
and when you jump onto My Kundalini, then

00:13:25.000 --> 00:13:26.634
there is no thought.

00:13:27.033 --> 00:13:32.087
You cannot think.

00:13:32.167 --> 00:13:36.501
When you think that, how much your Mother
loves you, you are jumping onto My Kundalini.

00:13:37.434 --> 00:13:40.200
And that time, there’s no thought.

00:13:41.200 --> 00:13:46.521
It’s very simple to meditate in Sahaja
Yoga because you have somebody in person.

00:13:46.601 --> 00:13:50.120
They never had somebody in person.

00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:52.287
So I can understand their problems:

00:13:52.367 --> 00:13:57.434
there was nobody in person; they had to do it in the air.

00:13:59.567 --> 00:14:05.521
But here, a sure-shot thing: you can feel your vibrations,

00:14:05.601 --> 00:14:13.567
you can feel My love, and you can feel your own quality.

00:14:17.033 --> 00:14:20.267
It’s very simple.

00:14:22.334 --> 00:14:27.287
But it’s not the love that is selfish,

00:14:27.367 --> 00:14:31.521
it’s not the love where you say, “Oh
Mother loves me so She’ll look after me,

00:14:31.601 --> 00:14:35.667
She’ll do everything for me, She’s going to do everything.”

00:14:38.601 --> 00:14:43.601
Is the love that, “Mother loves me so much, what can I do for Her?

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:48.667
Which is the best flower I can give to my Mother?

00:14:50.167 --> 00:14:52.454
What does She need? She needs nothing.

00:14:52.534 --> 00:14:57.087
She doesn’t need money, She doesn’t need anything.

00:14:57.167 --> 00:14:59.387
What can I give Her?

00:14:59.467 --> 00:15:01.587
Which is the best flower?”

00:15:01.667 --> 00:15:10.154
Like Shri Hanumana was given a gold necklace by Sitaji.

00:15:10.234 --> 00:15:14.053
And He saw that, and He was sitting on a tree

00:15:14.133 --> 00:15:23.601
and He was breaking one by one all of
those big, big gold balls of His necklace.

00:15:25.534 --> 00:15:28.320
So Sitaji said, “What are you doing?”

00:15:28.400 --> 00:15:34.354
He said, “I’m trying to see in these balls where is Ram.”

00:15:34.434 --> 00:15:42.320
He said, “None of them has, so I’m just breaking
them to find out. Otherwise why should I wear it?”

00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:45.354
And then She said, “Really? Where is Ram?”

00:15:45.434 --> 00:15:52.634
He opened His chest. He said, “See in My chest. He exists there.”

00:15:53.267 --> 00:15:56.154
So it is never a one-sided sort of a thing.

00:15:56.234 --> 00:16:02.320
It’s a thing that exists within you, and
you feel that and then has to be reciprocal.

00:16:02.400 --> 00:16:10.200
In the water, if there is a ripple it goes
to the shores and then it returns back.

00:16:16.434 --> 00:16:24.287
So with this force only, I tell you, you
can conquer your ego and superego, both.

00:16:24.367 --> 00:16:27.234
There’s no way out.

00:16:32.200 --> 00:16:40.634
And for these Indians it’s very easy to do
because, you see, they know their Mother’s love.

00:16:42.601 --> 00:16:48.187
I know there has been an attack on that
point and the mothers have been funny there.

00:16:48.267 --> 00:16:58.554
But doesn’t matter; when you see something,
just put yourself to it – to feel your roots.

00:16:58.634 --> 00:17:00.601
These are your roots.

00:17:01.000 --> 00:17:07.053
And then you see the enjoyment. The
Mother Earth Herself is sucking you down.

00:17:07.133 --> 00:17:09.434
She’s sucking you down.

00:17:14.200 --> 00:17:16.387
That is how you meditate now.

00:17:16.467 --> 00:17:22.554
This is how you have to meditate,
and it’s such a security-giving thing.

00:17:22.634 --> 00:17:26.320
It will change your expressions, faces, everything.

00:17:26.400 --> 00:17:35.267
And that enamoured expression that you find
in these people will be on your faces very soon.

00:17:41.367 --> 00:17:47.554
And complete silence will exist once you come on My Kundalini.

00:17:47.634 --> 00:17:59.234
But not through your mental projection, but
through your meditative, spontaneous experience.

00:18:01.133 --> 00:18:06.087
It’s very joy-giving. Just feel the joy of that.

00:18:06.167 --> 00:18:14.521
You are all with Me here, and the joy of
that feeling will really enlarge your hearts,

00:18:14.601 --> 00:18:18.667
and then you can give it to others.

00:18:20.434 --> 00:18:29.000
You don’t have to be crazy about these
things, but just to feel it within yourself.

00:18:33.300 --> 00:18:35.154
All right.

00:18:35.234 --> 00:18:42.220
Now I move on to Indians because they are a different style of people.

00:18:42.300 --> 00:18:44.534
May God bless you!

00:18:49.601 --> 00:18:52.534
(Marathi talk)

00:31:38.534 --> 00:31:40.454
Now, I was telling them, I must

00:31:40.534 --> 00:31:46.053
translate it to you in English is the most important point

00:31:46.133 --> 00:31:51.454
I was telling that now you are transformed,
now you have become saints, no doubt of it.

00:31:51.534 --> 00:31:54.387
Now from an egg you have become a bird,

00:31:54.467 --> 00:32:00.634
but, now what should happen to you?
Your Kundalini is still in the sacrum.

00:32:01.033 --> 00:32:06.120
How it has happened that now you have got all the Ganesha Shakti?

00:32:06.200 --> 00:32:12.421
I have made you like Ganesha, in the same
pattern as I had made Ganesha you are made.

00:32:12.501 --> 00:32:20.421
Now you have become a Ganesha, and from this Ganesha stage,

00:32:20.501 --> 00:32:30.020
which you think you are a Ganesha
now, if I offer you a throne of Shri Ganesha,

00:32:30.100 --> 00:32:35.354
if you have to sit on that throne as a king, then what should happen?

00:32:35.434 --> 00:32:40.554
Actually, that now your Kundalini
should not be anymore in the sacrum bone,

00:32:40.634 --> 00:32:45.601
but in your stomach, because Ganesha's Kundalini is in the stomach.

00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:49.120
In the stomach means in the Nabhi Chakra.

00:32:49.200 --> 00:32:55.521
Means all your seeking has been so far in materialism,

00:32:55.601 --> 00:33:01.320
has been in other things like in money, or in

00:33:01.400 --> 00:33:05.587
power or in love or whatever it was.

00:33:05.667 --> 00:33:11.120
But now your Kundalini itself is in the Nabhi Chakra, means

00:33:11.200 --> 00:33:16.053
your seeking is nothing but itself has become the Kundalini.

00:33:16.133 --> 00:33:22.287
Your seeking has become the Kundalini, means that you are the giver,

00:33:22.367 --> 00:33:26.220
now you are the Guru, you have now become the Guru.

00:33:26.300 --> 00:33:32.187
When the Kundalini starts from the
Nabhi that means now you are the Guru,

00:33:32.267 --> 00:33:38.454
now you have to give all the blessings,everything, as a Guru does.

00:33:38.534 --> 00:33:41.120
Now you all have become Gurus.

00:33:41.200 --> 00:33:44.187
But that's only possible when the Kundalini has risen,

00:33:44.267 --> 00:33:50.154
has lifted Her abode from the sacrum to the stomach,

00:33:50.234 --> 00:33:55.421
and this stage, unless and until it has
arrived, you are not a confirmed Guru.

00:33:55.501 --> 00:33:58.601
Once that has happened you become a Guru and then

00:33:59.000 --> 00:34:04.634
you can really impress people and work it out.

00:34:05.033 --> 00:34:07.120
It has to be done very fast.

00:34:07.200 --> 00:34:10.601
It has to work out very fast and for that, first of all,

00:34:11.000 --> 00:34:14.254
please get rid of your entanglements which are stupid.

00:34:14.334 --> 00:34:18.154
If you really believe that you have to progress in your seeking,

00:34:18.234 --> 00:34:23.120
that you have to have your Kundalini coming up from your Nabhi,

00:34:23.200 --> 00:34:30.667
then please, please hurry up, please try
to work out, otherwise you are very few who

00:34:31.067 --> 00:34:39.554
have been given also the privilege of doing My Puja, very few.

00:34:39.634 --> 00:34:42.654
And those who have been given have a chance

00:34:42.734 --> 00:34:46.354
to develop to that stage, and once you become that, all

00:34:46.434 --> 00:34:51.454
of you who have achieved that stage can become the Gurus.

00:34:51.534 --> 00:34:55.187
And for that, you have to have only wisdom.

00:34:55.267 --> 00:34:58.354
Wisdom, keep to your wisdom,

00:34:58.434 --> 00:35:04.120
and like Shri Ganesha has His wisdom and in that wisdom He knew

00:35:04.200 --> 00:35:07.187
one thing: that His Mother was all powerful

00:35:07.267 --> 00:35:11.587
and that He doesn't have to worship anybody else but His Mother.

00:35:11.667 --> 00:35:17.020
And He has to have all the powers which are granted by Her.

00:35:17.100 --> 00:35:22.454
His powers, no one, even Brahma, Vishnu, Mahesha does not have.

00:35:22.534 --> 00:35:24.654
They cannot reach Ganesha;

00:35:24.734 --> 00:35:28.387
They cannot reach His stage because They are one-sided but

00:35:28.467 --> 00:35:32.387
Shri Ganesha has all the powers, all the Chaitanya powers He has.

00:35:32.467 --> 00:35:36.354
So to become like that, to be like that,He should be your ideal:

00:35:36.434 --> 00:35:43.154
how He behaved and how He would
sacrifice anything for the sake of Mother.

00:35:43.234 --> 00:35:49.554
Here there are people who don't even
want to pay for something like a puja and ..stuff

00:35:49.634 --> 00:35:54.120
which you may just spend away somewhere in nonsensical things,

00:35:54.200 --> 00:35:58.187
because your attention has to be brought round completely.

00:35:58.267 --> 00:36:04.354
It has to be completely severed from
all these nonsensical entanglements

00:36:04.434 --> 00:36:08.634
and there should be less talking and more experiencing.

00:36:09.033 --> 00:36:13.053
Then only it's going to work out.

00:36:13.133 --> 00:36:21.521
It's a good pleasure and a great thing to be here in this holy land,

00:36:21.601 --> 00:36:25.120
it's a very holy place you can see it, so peaceful.

00:36:25.200 --> 00:36:28.087
Try to feel the peace within yourself that

00:36:28.167 --> 00:36:31.521
is within every human being and after

00:36:31.601 --> 00:36:33.487
that you have to know that this

00:36:33.567 --> 00:36:37.421
peace that you are achieving has to be given to others.

00:36:37.501 --> 00:36:43.020
In Sahaja Yoga, perhaps you have realized,
whatever you have got from the nature,

00:36:43.100 --> 00:36:45.454
you can release it back.

00:36:45.534 --> 00:36:50.587
For example if you give vibrations to a plant you can make it grow.

00:36:50.667 --> 00:36:56.421
If you give vibrations to a flower you can make it sustain its life.

00:36:56.501 --> 00:36:59.601
For the first time you are giving something to the nature,

00:37:00.000 --> 00:37:03.454
but as soon as you grow up to that state of a

00:37:03.534 --> 00:37:08.621
Guru then you can give the peace

00:37:08.701 --> 00:37:13.554
that is in the nature, you can give
the feeling of bliss that is in the nature.

00:37:13.634 --> 00:37:17.053
But first achieve it within yourself.

00:37:17.133 --> 00:37:23.454
Make this go inside you and see that bliss settle down within you.

00:37:23.534 --> 00:37:27.220
You don't see other nonsensical things which are very disturbing

00:37:27.300 --> 00:37:29.287
sometimes to your western mind.

00:37:29.367 --> 00:37:32.287
For example if a telephone is not working

00:37:32.367 --> 00:37:36.387
or the road is not all right, if the bathroom is not this.

00:37:36.467 --> 00:37:42.667
These nonsensical things have no meaning, but feel the peace outside,

00:37:43.067 --> 00:37:52.053
try to establish that peace within because
this peace you have to give to others.

00:37:52.133 --> 00:37:55.487
The whole development plan that I have is very fast

00:37:55.567 --> 00:37:58.554
and I am sure you will keep pace with me.

00:37:58.634 --> 00:38:00.154
So may God bless you!

00:38:00.234 --> 00:38:06.667
When you sit down just feel the peace
and try to achieve that peace within yourself.

00:38:07.067 --> 00:38:11.601
Don't pay attention to nonsensical
things and this with this your little

00:38:12.000 --> 00:38:16.487
brain trying to criticize, but try to
achieve the peace within yourself so

00:38:16.567 --> 00:38:20.020
that you can give peace to others.

00:38:20.100 --> 00:38:25.387
It's not proper that some of you are
looking after the negative people all the time,

00:38:25.467 --> 00:38:26.521
it's not proper.

00:38:26.601 --> 00:38:30.154
You don't have to look after the
negative people. Just leave them alone.

00:38:30.234 --> 00:38:34.120
Keep out of that because negative people can always bring you down.

00:38:34.200 --> 00:38:39.020
Don't try to improve the conditions of the
negative, leave them behind. You go fast.

00:38:39.100 --> 00:38:44.667
Once you have achieved that state
then we can arrange for them to come.

00:38:45.067 --> 00:38:49.020
For example, if My car has failed,
all right, I got into another car, which

00:38:49.100 --> 00:38:51.721
was all right because I have to come to the program.

00:38:51.801 --> 00:38:55.020
Then I can send the tempo from here to get that another

00:38:55.100 --> 00:38:59.554
car where there were some people who
were not supposed to be at the program.

00:38:59.634 --> 00:39:03.634
That's how you have to be quick and not bother your heads too much

00:39:04.033 --> 00:39:08.187
about the negative people who are
sick people, trying to be compassionate.

00:39:08.267 --> 00:39:10.953
There is no need. Tell them, tell Mother.

00:39:11.033 --> 00:39:12.187
Let you talk to Mother.

00:39:12.267 --> 00:39:15.521
Look after yourselves and don't be bothered about them.

00:39:15.601 --> 00:39:19.053
This is another nonsensical idea of compassion you have got.

00:39:19.133 --> 00:39:22.087
Compassion is not mental projection I told you:

00:39:22.167 --> 00:39:24.634
the compassion that works, that flows.

00:39:25.033 --> 00:39:28.601
It's all mental you see for us compassion is mental, every idea,

00:39:29.000 --> 00:39:34.354
peace is mental, bliss is mental, God
is mental, everything is mental for us.

00:39:34.434 --> 00:39:41.120
He is not. He is the one that resides in the heart as Spirit.

00:39:41.200 --> 00:39:43.521
He is the one who works through the compassion.

00:39:43.601 --> 00:39:49.587
And now you know My compassion is that it flows, it works, it acts.

00:39:49.667 --> 00:39:54.521
It's not mental.

00:39:54.601 --> 00:40:00.254
So don't try to be mentally concerned
with people and try to be compassionate.

00:40:00.334 --> 00:40:01.421
All right?

00:40:01.501 --> 00:40:05.587
I hope you understand that the compassion is not a mental idea

00:40:05.667 --> 00:40:10.187
that we are compassionate, we are
working for the unity of the world.And all that.

00:40:10.267 --> 00:40:15.587
Even unity and all those ideas, even
the idea of collective understanding

00:40:15.667 --> 00:40:20.220
is in the heart, it should work.

00:40:20.300 --> 00:40:23.587
In Sanskrit it is Kaaryanvit.

00:40:23.667 --> 00:40:27.020
In English there is no word. Kaaryanvit

00:40:27.100 --> 00:40:29.953
is embodied with the working capacity,

00:40:30.033 --> 00:40:32.554
embodied with the working out capacity

00:40:32.634 --> 00:40:34.587
actually "working out capacity"

00:40:34.667 --> 00:40:37.020
you can translate like that. It should work.

00:40:37.100 --> 00:40:41.187
If it does not work out then what's the
use of looking after somebody who is sick?

00:40:41.267 --> 00:40:46.053
all right, come along This is nonsense, this is very mental.

00:40:46.133 --> 00:40:54.220
Just don't waste your energy; you
have not come here to look after the sick.

00:40:54.300 --> 00:41:01.287
I hope you understand this idea of
looking after the sick and being very

00:41:01.367 --> 00:41:04.953
is all ego-oriented, see we are trying to help the sick,

00:41:05.033 --> 00:41:08.354
we are trying to help this, that,?all ego-oriented.

00:41:08.434 --> 00:41:13.053
Another superego-oriented that we are sacrificing this and that and

00:41:13.133 --> 00:41:16.287
we are becoming beggars in India like the Hare-Rama-Hare-Krishna.

00:41:16.367 --> 00:41:18.354
Beggars, parasites.

00:41:18.434 --> 00:41:21.487
Both are just the same, now please don't do all these things

00:41:21.567 --> 00:41:31.154
and try to keep yourself glued to one ideal:

00:41:31.234 --> 00:41:34.421
that you have to ascend faster.

00:41:34.501 --> 00:41:41.020
You have to individually ascend
faster and collectively pull out everyone

00:41:41.100 --> 00:41:45.521
but not those who are heavily laden with problems and

00:41:45.601 --> 00:41:49.120
who are creating problems and objecting your progress.

00:41:49.200 --> 00:41:53.020
That doesn't mean that you are not compassionate.

00:41:53.100 --> 00:41:59.087
You know how much compassion that I
have but My compassion doesn't make stories,

00:41:59.167 --> 00:42:02.154
I am so compassionate and I am this and that.

00:42:02.234 --> 00:42:04.120
Up to a point is all right but

00:42:04.200 --> 00:42:07.354
don't so too much
bother about people who are dragging you behind.

00:42:07.434 --> 00:42:09.667
You have come here for a training,

00:42:10.067 --> 00:42:18.220
a training into the understanding of awareness which is compassion.

00:42:18.300 --> 00:42:22.621
You all have to, even, when you go to the
school, you are not bothered about a person

00:42:22.701 --> 00:42:26.154
who is lacking in the class, do you?

00:42:26.234 --> 00:42:29.320
You want to study fast so that you come up well.

00:42:29.400 --> 00:42:32.287
In the same way, I would request you not to bother your

00:42:32.367 --> 00:42:36.320
heads too much about people who are trying to pull you down

00:42:36.400 --> 00:42:39.254
because I don't want you to be pulled down.

00:42:39.334 --> 00:42:44.521
That's My compassion for them and for you.

00:42:44.601 --> 00:42:49.087
Let Me look after them and you just don't worry your heads about them.

00:42:49.167 --> 00:42:51.087
They will be all right.

00:42:51.167 --> 00:42:52.721
So, may God bless you!

00:42:52.801 --> 00:42:59.554
Lets have a puja today, and this puja will be simple today.

00:42:59.634 --> 00:43:05.354
I think we will have Ganesha's Puja
and then we will have Devi's Puja today,

00:43:05.434 --> 00:43:12.200
and then we will have a good havan. That is a good place for havan.